tests.name: Dev Stamp Index stampInHtml should validate the browser environment when called.
Dev Stamp Index stampInHtml should call the comment mode when the mode is comment.
Dev Stamp Index stampInHtml should call the meta tag mode when the mode is meta-tag.
Dev Stamp Index stampInHtml should log an error when one of the stamp methods throws an error.
Dev Stamp Utils validateBrowserEnvironment should throw an error when not in a browser environment because window is undefined.
Dev Stamp Utils validateBrowserEnvironment should throw an error when not in a browser environment because document is undefined.
Dev Stamp Utils validateBrowserEnvironment should not throw an error when in a browser environment.
Dev Stamp Utils getTargetElement should throw an error when the target element is not found.
Dev Stamp Utils getTargetElement should return the target element when it is found.
Dev Stamp Utils getStampOptions should return default options when no options are provided.
Dev Stamp Utils getStampOptions should override default options with provided options when called.
Meta Tag Mode stampOnExistingMetaTag should set the content attribute of the existing meta tag to the message when overwrite is true.
Meta Tag Mode stampOnExistingMetaTag should log an error when overwrite is false.
Meta Tag Mode stampMetaTagInHtml should create a new meta tag with the message when there is no existing meta tag.
Meta Tag Mode stampMetaTagInHtml should call stampOnExistingMetaTag when there is an existing meta tag.
Comment Mode stampCommentInHtml should get the target element when called.
Comment Mode stampCommentInHtml should create comment node with the message when called.
